Christine Lynn Smith was arrested on Tuesday after the bodies of 10 dogs and three cats were found decaying in her home in Macon, Georgia . 
  The home had been auctioned off and was littered with over 1,000 empty beer cans  . 
  Smith worked at a local animal shelter for two months in 2012 but was fired after six months . 
  She was charged with 13 counts of animal cruelty . 
 